-- negative view that people already probably

23:01.380 --> 23:02.982 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
already have towards Muslims.

23:03.015 --> 23:07.186 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
P.J. TOBIA: The vitriol has even been felt
outside of Muslim communities. In Manassas,

23:07.219 --> 23:12.157 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Virginia, about 30 miles West of Washington,
D.C., the local mosque has been repeatedly

23:12.191 --> 23:16.095 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
