23:16.128 --> 23:21.267 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It has made some non-Muslim residents more
than a little uncomfortable. Patty Reed works

23:21.300 --> 23:22.901 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
at a local hardware store.

23:22.935 --> 23:25.704 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
PATTY REED, Virginia: Gosh, it just makes
us look like a bunch of rednecks. I'm going

23:25.738 --> 23:30.609 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to be honest. And I don't like it. Why we
wouldn't be able to talk to these people,

23:30.643 --> 23:32.845 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
talk to -- you know, voice our concerns?

23:32.878 --> 23:37.049 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
P.J. TOBIA: But many are scared, saying recent
events have them on edge.

23:37.082 --> 23:40.886 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN: If you're somebody who is doing the
right thing and you're here in the right way,

23:40.919 --> 23:45.157 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
then it truly isn't fair to you. But things
happen. You know, it isn't fair to us what's

23:45.190 --> 23:51.130 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
going on either, but -- or those people that
died, but it's what's going on in the world

23:51.163 --> 23:52.831 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
today.

23:52.865 --> 23:56.802 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
